id: pm-x878
title: "CI: make Codecov badge uploads branch-explicit"
description: README Codecov badge briefly rendered unknown even though CODECOV_TOKEN is configured. Harden CI uploads and badge URLs so Codecov receives explicit branch/commit metadata for the default branch and the README badge points at main directly.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[3]: "area:ci","area:coverage",codecov
created_at: "2026-06-26T15:22:45.840Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-26T16:28:41.181Z"
author: codex-sdk-cli-continuation
parent: pm-u9d0
resolution: Pinned README Codecov badge to the main-branch badge URL and sent explicit branch/commit metadata in CI uploads.
expected_result: README badge no longer renders unknown and CI workflow contracts protect Codecov upload metadata.
actual_result: "Branch-pinned badge returned a 100% SVG; workflow contract, typecheck, static quality, coverage, release gates, and temp smoke passed."
