  "2026-06-26T15:52:00.738Z",codex,"Follow-up evidence: merged current main, regenerated CHANGELOG.md with pm-changelog 2026.6.20 after closing pm-x878/pm-m8yl/pm-xsth, verified pnpm changelog:pm:check, pnpm quality:static, ci workflow contract test, and live branch-pinned Codecov badge returns 100%."
  "2026-06-26T16:28:41.181Z",codex,"Review follow-up: removed the live Codecov curl from linked tests after cubic flagged external network dependency. The live badge check remains evidence in comments; the linked test list now uses the sandbox-safe CI workflow contract test."
